This folder contains all the scripts for running step2
Step 2 is basically just retrieving all the crispr and Cas annotations
from
scratchCM/tmp_projects/epasolli_darkmatter/allcontigs/ZellerG_2014/metabat/genomes_comp50_cont05/prokka/<dataset__sample__bin>/<dataset__sample__bin.gff>
and saving them inside
$data/2casanno/crisprcasanno
and, further filtering for just the proteins (neglecting CRISPR repeats) and saving them in
$data/2casanno/justcasanno
and filtering for just minced, che forse l'ho fatto 'a mano' da bash, senza salvarmi lo script, oh well non Ã¨ niente di trascendentale

maybe redundant, but, oh well.
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
FILES 
|
|-retrieve_all_annotations.py                 # executes step2 for all datasets
|-retrieve_annotations_of_dataset.py          # executes step2 for a given dataset
|-retrieve_minced_annotations_of_dataset.py   # executes step2 for a given dataset, but only retrieves CRISPRrepeats  information
|-parall.sh                                # just a for loop to iterate retrieve_annotations_of_dataset.py on all datasets
|-README                                   # this file, lol.
